ftc.team6460.javadeck.api.planner.geom

Class Field

  • java.lang.Object
    • ftc.team6460.javadeck.api.planner.geom.Field

  • public class Field
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes a field of waypoints and zones that a robot may navigate.

    Dimensions are fixed-point decimal, defined such that a value of 1 describes an offset of 1mm.
